待《星際奇兵：亞特蘭提斯》第四季的結束，他將自己的[[辮子|辮子]]剪去。摩莫亞為戲而留的辮子讓他感覺有些頭疼，在第五季的「{{lang|en|Broken Ties}}」一集中他將此長髮切除。在拍攝了第5季的第一天，他的辮子被重新接回，但在過程中過於繁重，使他改以{{link-en|特效替身|Stunt double}}的方式使用假髮，直到兩週後才拿到訂製的假髮<ref>{{cite web | author=Sumner, Darren | url=http://www.gateworld.net/news/2008/05/momoa_the_dreads_stay_put.shtml | title=Momoa: The Dreads Stay Put | publisher=[[Gateworld|Gateworld]] | date=2008-05-26 | accessdate=2011-08-18 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080711051533/http://www.gateworld.net/news/2008/05/momoa_the_dreads_stay_put.shtml | archivedate=2008-07-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author=Sumner, Darren | url=http://www.gateworld.net/news/2008/02/new_plot_details_on_broken_ties.shtml | title=New Plot Details on 'Broken Ties' | publisher=[[Gateworld|Gateworld]] | date=2008-02-23 | accessdate=2011-08-18 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616084801/http://www.gateworld.net/news/2008/02/new_plot_details_on_broken_ties.shtml | archivedate=2011-06-16 }}</ref>。值得一提的是，當他第一次詮釋角色時，製片人要求他將長髮剪掉，但這卻成為了此角色的象徵，於是製片方允許摩莫亞將長髮留住。

[[劇情片|劇情]][[驚悚片|驚悚片]]《{{link-en|漫漫復仇路|Road to Paloma}}》（2014年）是摩莫亞首部導演的長片作品，主演包括摩莫亞、[[莎拉·夏希|莎拉·夏希]]、{{link-en|麗莎·博內特|Lisa Bonet}}、[[麥可·雷蒙德-詹姆斯|麥可·雷蒙德-詹姆斯]]和[[韋恩·斯塔蒂|韋恩·斯塔蒂]]<ref name=Jason>{{cite web| title=Jason Momoa Talks CONAN; Reveals He’s Writing and Directing ROAD TO PALOMA| url=http://collider.com/jason-momoa-conan-road-to-paloma-interview/| publisher=collider.com| accessdate=2013-08-14| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131221200617/http://collider.com/jason-momoa-conan-road-to-paloma-interview/| archive-date=2013-12-21| dead-url=no}}</ref>，於2014年4月在{{link-en|薩拉索塔電影節|Sarasota Film Festival}}首映<ref>{{cite web |author=Gordon Cox Legit Editor @GCoxVariety |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jason-momoas-road-to-paloma-to-premiere-in-2014-sarasota-film-festival-1201130089/ |title=Jason Momoa’s ‘Road to Paloma’ to Premiere at Sarasota Film Festival |publisher=Variety |date=2014-03-12 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024070817/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jason-momoas-road-to-paloma-to-premiere-in-2014-sarasota-film-festival-1201130089/ |archive-date=2014-10-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本片只於2014年7月15日美國[[有限上映|有限上映]]，[[紐約市|紐約市]]和[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]則只有[[VOD|VOD]]版本<ref>{{cite web |last=Schwartz |first=Terri |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2014/02/jason-momoa-landed-the-red-road-thanks-to-his-directorial-debut-road-to-paloma.html |title=Jason Momoa landed 'The Red Road' thanks to his directorial debut 'Road to Paloma' - Zap2it | News & Features |publisher=Blog.zap2it.com |date=2014-02-26 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302181100/http://blog.zap2it.com/pop2it/2014/02/jason-momoa-landed-the-red-road-thanks-to-his-directorial-debut-road-to-paloma.html |archivedate=2014-03-02 }}</ref>。

2014年3月，摩莫亞加入了與[[凱瑞·艾文斯|凱瑞·艾文斯]]、{{link-en|海莉·韋伯|Haley Webb}}共同演出的黑色驚悚喜劇片《{{link-en|糖山 (電影)|Sugar Mountain (film)|糖山}}》，主要拍攝於[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115943 |title=Cary Elwes and Jason Momoa to Climb Sugar Mountain |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2014-03-12 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021133749/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=115943 |archive-date=2014-10-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cary-elwes-jason-momoa-join-688082 |title=Cary Elwes, Jason Momoa Join Indie 'Sugar Mountain' |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |date=2014-03-12 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903130651/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cary-elwes-jason-momoa-join-688082 |archive-date=2014-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年6月有報導說，摩莫亞已被引入2016年的[[超級英雄電影|超級英雄電影]]《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》中詮釋[[水行俠|亞瑟·庫瑞／水行俠]]，但此消息並未獲得官方人士的證實<ref name="JasonMomoaAquaman">{{cite news |last=Sciretta |first=Peter |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/aquaman-jason-momoa-batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice/ |title=Jason Momoa Is Aquaman in ‘Batman V Superman: Dawn Of Justice’ |accessdate=2014-06-14 |newspaper=[[杰森·莫玛/Film|杰森·莫玛//Film]] |date=2014-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140615171017/http://www.slashfilm.com/aquaman-jason-momoa-batman-v-superman-dawn-of-justice/ |archive-date=2014-06-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="JasonMomoaAquaman2">{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/jason-momoa-will-play-aquaman-in-dawn-of-justice-and-we-know-how-it-will-happen|title=JASON MOMOA WILL PLAY AQUAMAN IN 'DAWN OF JUSTICE,' AND WE KNOW HOW IT WILL HAPPEN|last=McWeeny|first=Drew|work=Hitfix|date=2014-06-14|accessdate=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018195433/http://www.hitfix.com/motion-captured/jason-momoa-will-play-aquaman-in-dawn-of-justice-and-we-know-how-it-will-happen|archive-date=2014-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="JasonMomoaAquaman3">{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jason-momoa-playing-aquaman-batman-711899|title=Jason Momoa to Play Aquaman in 'Batman v. Superman: Dawn of Justice'|authors=Rebecca Ford and Borys Kit|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-06-16|accessdate=2014-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140618182615/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jason-momoa-playing-aquaman-batman-711899|archive-date=2014-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當於他在《[[吉米·金莫直播秀|吉米·金莫直播秀]]》上被問及此消息時，摩莫亞回應：「這些都是謠言」<ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2662929/Game-Of-Thrones-star-Jason-Momoa-remains-coy-grilled-playing-Aquaman-Man-Of-Steel-sequel.html 'Those are rumours': Game Of Thrones star Jason Momoa remains coy when grilled about playing Aquaman in Man Of Steel sequel] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2662929/Game-Of-Thrones-star-Jason-Momoa-remains-coy-grilled-playing-Aquaman-Man-Of-Steel-sequel.html |date=20140809095737 }} by [[Helen_Zhao|Helen Zhao]], UK Daily Mail, 2014-06-19</ref>。2014年10月，摩莫亞將飾演水行俠的傳聞被[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]證實是真的，且他還將在《[[水行俠_(電影)|水行俠]]》中擔任主演<ref name="aquabat">{{cite web|url=http://screenrant.com/aquaman-movie-actor-jason-momoa-official/|title=It’s Official: Jason Momoa is ‘Aquaman’; Solo Movie Coming 2018|author=|date=2014-10-15|work=Screen Rant|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017063046/http://screenrant.com/aquaman-movie-actor-jason-momoa-official/|archive-date=2014-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|title=Warner Bros Massive DC Movie Slate Revealed - /Film|author=|date=|work=Slashfilm|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6TQ91KdDF?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/dc-movie-slate-revealed/|archive-date=2014-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《水行俠》於2018年上映並取得成功的口碑。

