== 個人生活 ==
摩莫亞曾四處旅行，如在[[巴黎|巴黎]]拿起蠟筆畫畫、在[[西藏|西藏]]學習佛法<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ca.movies.yahoo.com/person/jason-momoa/biography.html |title=Jason Momoa Biography - Yahoo Movies Canada |publisher=Ca.movies.yahoo.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140304051819/http://ca.movies.yahoo.com/person/jason-momoa/biography.html |archivedate=2014-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.starpulse.com/Actors/Momoa,_Jason/Biography/ |title=Jason Momoa Biography |publisher=Starpulse.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022235921/http://www.starpulse.com/Actors/Momoa,_Jason/Biography/ |archive-date=2013-10-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。摩莫亞是澳式足球俱樂部{{link-en|阿德雷德港足球俱樂部|Port Adelaide Football Club}}的粉絲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thirat-atthiraride.tumblr.com/post/97463937249/i-wasnt-going-to-see-jason-again-but-i-found-out|title=Thirat Atthiraride|author=|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029233622/http://thirat-atthiraride.tumblr.com/post/97463937249/i-wasnt-going-to-see-jason-again-but-i-found-out|archive-date=2014-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2005年，經過共同朋友的介紹下摩莫亞認識了女演員{{link-en|麗莎·博內特|Lisa Bonet}}，他第一眼看到麗莎已被她深深吸引，並認定麗莎是他的終生伴侶，繼而展開追求。2007年7月23日，他和博內特有了女兒蘿拉·伊奧拉尼·莫瑪（{{lang|en|Lola Iolani Momoa}}）。他與博內特後來生了一個兒子諾加-沃夫·曼庫帕·那卡哈·摩莫亞（{{lang|en|Nakoa-Wolf Manakauapo Namakaeha Momoa}}），於2008年12月15日出生。摩莫亞的母親在摩莫亞的官方網站上的粉絲論壇公布，「{{lang|en|Nakoa}}」的意思是「勇士」（儘管這詞代表著是「勇氣」），而「{{lang|en|Kaua}}」（雨）和「{{lang|en|Po}}」（黑暗）則取於他出生的那天（他晚上出生在洛杉磯時有著罕見的惡劣天氣）。中間名「{{lang|en|Namakaeha}}」（那卡哈）則是取自他的父親<ref>{{cite web |author = Staff |date = 2009-01-09 |url = http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/28584888/ns/today-entertainment/t/lisa-bonets-new-babys-name-mouthful |title = Lisa Bonet's New Baby's Name Is a Mouthful – Newborn Boy's Name Is Nakoa-Wolf Manakauapo Namakaeha Momoa |publisher = ''[[Access_Hollywood|Access Hollywood]]'' (via [[MSNBC|MSNBC]]) |accessdate = 2011-08-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111003194203/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/28584888/ns/today-entertainment/t/lisa-bonets-new-babys-name-mouthful |archive-date = 2011-10-03 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

雖然外界普遍認為摩莫亞和博內特是於2007年11月15日結婚，但這對夫妻直到2017年10月才正式辦理結婚<ref name=“UsWeekly(2017-11-02)”>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/jason-momoa-lisa-bonet-officially-marry-in-secret-wedding/|title=Jason Momoa, Lisa Bonet Officially Marry in Secret Wedding|date=2017-11-02|work=Us Weekly|access-date=2017-11-02|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171103060339/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/jason-momoa-lisa-bonet-officially-marry-in-secret-wedding/|archive-date=2017-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於摩莫亞和博內特結婚，使他成為了[[柔伊·克拉維茲|柔伊·克拉維茲]]的繼父<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/07/09/jason-momoa-lisa-bonet_n_5570751.html|title=Jason Momoa Gushing About Wife Lisa Bonet Couldn't Be More Adorable|last=Live|first=Emily Tess Katz HuffPost|date=2014-07-09|website=The Huffington Post|access-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628153550/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/07/09/jason-momoa-lisa-bonet_n_5570751.html|archive-date=2016-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2022年1月，他和博內特的婚姻宣告結束、已分居<ref>{{cite news |last1=France |first1=Lisa Respers |title=Jason Momoa and Lisa Bonet announce split |url=https://www.cnn.com/2022/01/12/entertainment/jason-momoa-lisa-bonet-split/index.html |publisher=CNN |date=2022-01-12}}</ref>。

2008年11月15日，摩莫亞在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[好萊塢|好萊塢]]的一間小酒館{{lang|en|Birds Cafe}}中被一名男子用破碎的啤酒杯弄傷了臉<ref name="NBC1">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Man Pleads Not Guilty To Assaulting 'Stargate Atlantis' Actor |url=http://www.nbclosangeles.com/news/entertainment/Man-Pleads-Not-Guilty-to-Assaulting-Stargate-Atlantis-Actor.html |publisher=[[KNBC|KNBC]] |date=2009-01-26 |accessdate=2011-08-18 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HygxyYee?url=http://www.nbclosangeles.com/entertainment/celebrity/Man-Pleads-Not-Guilty-to-Assaulting-Stargate-Atlantis-Actor.html |archive-date=2013-07-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=latimes>{{cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/10/5year-sentence-for-man-who-attacked-stargate-atalantis-actor-who-required-140-stitches.html|title=Winton, Richard ''Los Angeles Times'' October 7, 2009|author=|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009235457/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/10/5year-sentence-for-man-who-attacked-stargate-atalantis-actor-who-required-140-stitches.html|archive-date=2014-10-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他事後接受了140針的手術，這使得在他後來的作品中能明顯看出臉上的疤痕<ref name="NBC1"/>。這名攻擊者因襲擊罪而被判入獄五年<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/10/5year-sentence-for-man-who-attacked-stargate-atalantis-actor-who-required-140-stitches.html |title = Five-year sentence for man who attacked 'Stargate Atlantis' actor Jason Momoa |date = 2009-10-07 |publisher = Los Angeles Times |language = en |access-date = 2019-08-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190820155701/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2009/10/5year-sentence-for-man-who-attacked-stargate-atalantis-actor-who-required-140-stitches.html |archive-date = 2019-08-20 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

